<lb n="0578a12" ed="T"/><cb:juan n="001" fun="open"><cb:mulu n="001" type="卷"/><cb:jhead><note n="0578001" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">【原】麗本，【甲】黃檗版淨嚴等校訂加筆本</note>佛說一切如來金剛壽命陀羅尼
<lb n="0578a13" ed="T"/>經</cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<lb n="0578a14" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0578a15" ed="T"/><byline cb:type="Translator"><note n="0578002" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（開府…空）四十三字＝（南天竺國三藏金剛智共沙門智藏）十四字【宋】【元】，（唐南天竺國三藏金剛智共沙門智藏）十五字【明】【甲】</note><note n="0578002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（開府…空）四十三字【大】，南天竺國三藏金剛智共沙門智藏【宋】【元】，唐南天竺國三藏金剛智共沙門智藏【明】【甲】</note><app cb:word-count="43" n="0578002"><lem wit="【大】">開府儀同三司特進試鴻臚卿肅國
<lb n="0578a16" ed="T"/>公食邑三千戶賜紫贈司空諡大鑑
<lb n="0578a17" ed="T"/>正號大廣智大興善寺三藏沙門
<lb n="0578a18" ed="T"/>不空</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】">南天竺國三藏金剛智共沙門智藏</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【甲】">唐南天竺國三藏金剛智共沙門智藏</rdg></app>奉　詔譯</byline>
<lb n="0578a19" ed="T"/><cb:div type="jing"><p xml:id="pT20p0578a1901">如是我聞。一時佛<note n="0578003" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">在＝住【三】【甲】</note><note n="0578003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">在【大】，住【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0578003"><lem wit="【大】">在</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">住</rdg></app>殑伽河側。與諸比丘及
<lb n="0578a20" ed="T"/>大菩薩無量天人大眾俱。爾時世尊告毘沙
<lb n="0578a21" ed="T"/>門等四天王言。有四種法甚可怖畏。若男若
<lb n="0578a22" ed="T"/>女童男童女。一切有情無能免者。所謂生老
<lb n="0578a23" ed="T"/>病死。於中一法最為<note n="0578004" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">遍＝逼【三】【甲】</note><note n="0578004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">遍【大】，逼【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0578004"><lem wit="【大】">遍</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">逼</rdg></app>惱。難可對治。所謂
<lb n="0578a24" ed="T"/>死怖。我愍是故說對治法。爾時四天王白佛
<lb n="0578a25" ed="T"/>言。世尊我於今日為獲大利。<note n="0578005" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">唯＝惟【三】【甲】</note><note n="0578005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">唯【大】，惟【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0578005"><lem wit="【大】">唯</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">惟</rdg></app>願世尊為眾
<lb n="0578a26" ed="T"/>生故宣說是法。爾時世尊面向東方。彈指召
<lb n="0578a27" ed="T"/>集一切如來。作是誓言。所有十方一切如來
<lb n="0578a28" ed="T"/>應正等覺。為眾生故。證菩提者咸皆助我。令
<lb n="0578a29" ed="T"/>我以一切如來威神力故。悉<note n="0578006" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">令＋（如是）【三】【甲】</note><note n="0578006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">令【大】，令如是【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0578006"><lem wit="【大】">令</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">令如是</rdg></app>一切眾生轉
<pb n="0578b" xml:id="T20.1135.0578b" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0578b01" ed="T"/>非命業。使增壽命。我昔未為眾生轉此法輪。
<lb n="0578b02" ed="T"/>於今方轉。能令眾生壽命色力皆得成就無
<lb n="0578b03" ed="T"/>夭死怖。如是南西北方四維上下。召集<note n="0578007" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">驚＝警【三】【甲】</note><note n="0578007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">驚【大】，警【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0578007"><lem wit="【大】">驚</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">警</rdg></app>告
<lb n="0578b04" ed="T"/>亦復如是。爾時十方盡佛眼所到。若干世界
<lb n="0578b05" ed="T"/>一切如來皆悉赴集。遍滿虛空數如微塵。爾
<lb n="0578b06" ed="T"/>時一切諸佛為加持故。異口同音。即說一切
<lb n="0578b07" ed="T"/>如來金剛壽命陀羅尼曰。</p>
<lb n="0578b08" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0578b0801" cb:type="dharani">怛<note n="0578008" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">胵＝儞也二合去引【宋】【元】，儞也去聲二合引【明】【甲】</note><note n="0578008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">胵【大】，儞也二合去引【宋】【元】，儞也去聲二合引【明】【甲】</note><app n="0578008"><lem wit="【大】">胵</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】">儞也二合去引</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【甲】">儞也去聲二合引</rdg></app>他<note place="inline">一</note>者犁<note place="inline">二</note>者<note n="0578009" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">攞＋（引）細註【三】【甲】</note><note n="0578009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">攞【大】，攞(引)【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0578009"><lem wit="【大】">攞</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">攞<note place="inline">引</note></rdg></app>者犁<note place="inline">三</note><note n="0578010" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">彌娜知＝尾娜胝【三】【甲】</note><note n="0578010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">彌娜知【大】，尾娜胝【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0578010"><lem wit="【大】">彌娜知</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">尾娜胝</rdg></app>薩嚩
<lb n="0578b09" ed="T"/><note place="inline">二合</note>薩底<note place="inline">二合</note>稽<note place="inline">四</note>斫訖浪<note place="inline">二合</note>蘖<note n="0578011" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">南＝喃【三】【甲】＊</note><note n="0578011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">南【大】＊，喃【宋】【元】【明】【甲】＊</note><app n="0578011"><lem wit="【大】">南</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">喃</rdg></app><note place="inline">五</note>鉢囉<note place="inline">二合</note>
<lb n="0578b10" ed="T"/>舍滿<note n="0578012" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">都＋（六）細註【三】【甲】</note><note n="0578012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">都【大】，都(六)【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0578012"><lem wit="【大】">都</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">都<note place="inline">六</note></rdg></app>薩<note n="0578013" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">婆路誐六薩婆＝嚩路引誐薩嚩【三】【甲】</note><note n="0578013" resp="CBETA" type="mod">婆路誐六薩婆【大】，嚩路引誐薩嚩【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0578013"><lem wit="【大】">婆路誐<note place="inline">六</note>薩婆</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">嚩路引誐薩嚩</rdg></app>薩怛嚩<note place="inline">二合</note><app type="star" corresp="#0578011"><lem wit="【大】">南</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">喃</rdg></app><note place="inline">七</note>
<lb n="0578b11" ed="T"/>阿娜<note n="0578014" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">𪘜＝𪘨知解反八【宋】【元】，𪘨知解切八【明】【甲】</note><note n="0578014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">𪘜【大】，𪘨知解反八【宋】【元】，𪘨知解切八【明】【甲】</note><app n="0578014"><lem wit="【大】">𪘜</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】">𪘨知解反八</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【甲】">𪘨知解切八</rdg></app><note place="inline">八</note>俱娜𪘨<note place="inline">九</note><note n="0578015" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（遮㘑…反）十一字＝（摩賀娜𪘨十者㘑者㘑係麼澆）十二字【三】【甲】</note><note n="0578015" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（遮㘑…反）十一字【大】，摩賀娜𪘨十者㘑者㘑係麼澆【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app cb:word-count="11" n="0578015"><lem wit="【大】">遮㘑遮㘑<note place="inline">十</note>係麼澆<note place="inline">牛矯反</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">摩賀娜𪘨十者㘑者㘑係麼澆</rdg></app>
<lb n="0578b12" ed="T"/>哩<note place="inline">十一</note>係麼儞鏟<note n="0578016" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">尼＋（去）細註【宋】【元】，（去聲）細註【明】【甲】</note><note n="0578016" resp="CBETA" type="mod">尼【大】，尼(去)【宋】【元】，<!--CBETA todo type: newmod-->尼(去聲)【明】【甲】</note><app n="0578016"><lem wit="【大】">尼</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】">尼<note place="inline">去</note></rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【甲】">尼<note place="inline">去聲</note></rdg></app><note place="inline">十二</note>係麼尸棄<note place="inline">十三</note>矯囉微
<lb n="0578b13" ed="T"/><note place="inline">十四</note>矯囉<note n="0578017" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">迷＝䜝【三】【甲】</note><note n="0578017" resp="CBETA" type="mod">迷【大】，䜝【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0578017"><lem wit="【大】">迷</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">䜝</rdg></app><note place="inline">十五</note>係俱囉微<note place="inline">十六</note>信囉𠼐<note place="inline">十七</note>俱
<lb n="0578b14" ed="T"/>麼底<note place="inline">十八</note>微捨麼<note n="0578018" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">抳＋（麼抳）【三】【甲】</note><note n="0578018" resp="CBETA" type="mod">抳【大】，抳麼抳【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0578018"><lem wit="【大】">抳</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">抳麼抳</rdg></app><note place="inline">十九</note><note n="0578019" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">戍戍＝戌戌【三】【甲】</note><note n="0578019" resp="CBETA" type="mod">戍戍【大】，戌戌【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0578019"><lem wit="【大】">戍戍</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">戌戌</rdg></app><note n="0578020" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">毘＋（引）細註【三】【甲】</note><note n="0578020" resp="CBETA" type="mod">毘【大】，毘(引)【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0578020"><lem wit="【大】">毘</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">毘<note place="inline">引</note></rdg></app>嚩<note place="inline">二十</note>阿者
<lb n="0578b15" ed="T"/>犁<note place="inline">二十一</note>彌者犁<note place="inline">二十二</note>麼尾<note n="0578021" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">覽＝囕【三】【甲】</note><note n="0578021" resp="CBETA" type="mod">覽【大】，囕【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0578021"><lem wit="【大】">覽</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">囕</rdg></app>麼<note place="inline">二十三</note>戶<note n="0578022" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">毛＝謩【三】【甲】＊</note><note n="0578022" resp="CBETA" type="mod">毛【大】＊，謩【宋】【元】【明】【甲】＊</note><app n="0578022"><lem wit="【大】">毛</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">謩</rdg></app>戶
<lb n="0578b16" ed="T"/><app type="star" corresp="#0578022"><lem wit="【大】">毛</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">謩</rdg></app><note place="inline">二十四</note>唵<note n="0578023" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">二十五麼折囉＝嚩曰囉二合【三】【甲】</note><note n="0578023" resp="CBETA" type="mod">二十五麼折囉【大】，嚩曰囉二合【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0578023"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">二十五</note>麼折囉</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">嚩曰囉二合</rdg></app>諭<note n="0578024" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">師＝曬【三】【甲】</note><note n="0578024" resp="CBETA" type="mod">師【大】，曬【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0578024"><lem wit="【大】">師</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">曬</rdg></app><note place="inline">某甲<note n="0578025" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔二十六〕－【三】【甲】</note><note n="0578025" resp="CBETA" type="mod">二十六【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0578025"><lem wit="【大】">二十六</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app></note>薩嚩
<lb n="0578b17" ed="T"/><note n="0578026" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">訶＝二合賀引二十五【三】【甲】</note><note n="0578026" resp="CBETA" type="mod">訶【大】，二合賀引二十五【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0578026"><lem wit="【大】">訶</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">二合賀引二十五</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0578b18" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0578b1801">爾時十方佛所。一切執金剛菩薩異口同音
<lb n="0578b19" ed="T"/>亦說延命陀羅尼曰。</p>
<lb n="0578b20" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0578b2001" cb:type="dharani">吽<note n="0578027" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔引〕－【三】【甲】＊</note><note n="0578027" resp="CBETA" type="mod"><!--CBETA todo type: ＊-->引【大】＊，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】【甲】＊</note><app n="0578027"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">引</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>吽<note place="inline">引</note>尸棄薩嚩<note place="inline"><note n="0578028" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">二合引＝引二合【三】【甲】</note><note n="0578028" resp="CBETA" type="mod">二合引【大】，引二合【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0578028"><lem wit="【大】">二合引</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">引二合</rdg></app></note><note n="0578029" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">訶引＝賀一引【宋】，賀引【元】，賀引一【明】【甲】</note><note n="0578029" resp="CBETA" type="mod">訶引【大】，賀一引【宋】，賀引【元】，賀引一【明】【甲】</note><app n="0578029"><lem wit="【大】">訶<note place="inline">引</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">賀一引</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】">賀引</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【甲】">賀引一</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0578b21" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0578b2101">如是一切如來及十方執金剛菩薩。說是陀
<lb n="0578b22" ed="T"/>羅尼已隱而不現。</p>
<lb n="0578b23" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0578b2301">爾時毘沙門天王白佛言。我<note n="0578030" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔亦〕－【三】【甲】＊</note><note n="0578030" resp="CBETA" type="mod">亦【大】＊，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】【甲】＊</note><app n="0578030"><lem wit="【大】">亦</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>以佛神力。為
<lb n="0578b24" ed="T"/>一切眾生加持護念。除非命故說陀羅<note n="0578031" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">尼＋（曰）【三】【甲】＊</note><note n="0578031" resp="CBETA" type="mod">尼【大】＊，尼曰【宋】【元】【明】【甲】＊</note><app n="0578031"><lem wit="【大】">尼</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">尼曰</rdg></app>。</p>
<lb n="0578b25" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0578b2501" cb:type="dharani">始尾<note place="inline">二合<note n="0578032" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔下同〕－【三】【甲】</note><note n="0578032" resp="CBETA" type="mod">下同【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0578032"><lem wit="【大】">下同</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app></note>帝<note place="inline">一</note>始<note n="0578033" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">尾＋（二合）細註【三】【甲】</note><note n="0578033" resp="CBETA" type="mod">尾【大】，尾(二合)【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0578033"><lem wit="【大】">尾</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">尾<note place="inline">二合</note></rdg></app>怛犁<note place="inline">二</note>栗<note n="0578034" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">利＋（三）細註【三】【甲】</note><note n="0578034" resp="CBETA" type="mod">利【大】，利(三)【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0578034"><lem wit="【大】">利</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">利<note place="inline">三</note></rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0578b26" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0578b2601">爾時毘樓勒叉天王又白佛言。我<app type="star" corresp="#0578030"><lem wit="【大】">亦</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>以佛神
<lb n="0578b27" ed="T"/><note n="0578035" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">力＋（故）【三】【甲】</note><note n="0578035" resp="CBETA" type="mod">力【大】，力故【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0578035"><lem wit="【大】">力</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">力故</rdg></app>。為多眾生除夭命故。說陀<note n="0578036" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">囉＝羅【三】【甲】</note><note n="0578036" resp="CBETA" type="mod">囉【大】，羅【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0578036"><lem wit="【大】">囉</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">羅</rdg></app><app type="star" corresp="#0578031"><lem wit="【大】">尼</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">尼曰</rdg></app>。</p>
<lb n="0578b28" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0578b2801" cb:type="dharani">摩<note n="0578037" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">登＝蹬【三】【甲】</note><note n="0578037" resp="CBETA" type="mod">登【大】，蹬【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0578037"><lem wit="【大】">登</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">蹬</rdg></app>霓<note n="0578038" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔一〕－【三】【甲】</note><note n="0578038" resp="CBETA" type="mod">一【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0578038"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">一</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>摩<note n="0578039" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">登儗尼二＝蹬倪尼一【三】【甲】</note><note n="0578039" resp="CBETA" type="mod">登儗尼二【大】，蹬倪尼一【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0578039"><lem wit="【大】">登儗尼<note place="inline">二</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">蹬倪尼一</rdg></app>輸<note n="0578040" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">麼輸麼＝摩輸【三】【甲】</note><note n="0578040" resp="CBETA" type="mod">麼輸麼【大】，摩輸【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0578040"><lem wit="【大】">麼輸麼</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">摩輸</rdg></app>謀<note place="inline"><note n="0578041" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">三＝二【三】【甲】</note><note n="0578041" resp="CBETA" type="mod">三【大】，二【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0578041"><lem wit="【大】">三</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">二</rdg></app></note></p>
<lb n="0578b29" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0578b2901">爾時提頭賴吒天王亦白佛言。我亦為諸眾
<pb n="0578c" xml:id="T20.1135.0578c" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0578c01" ed="T"/>生。除死怖故說陀羅<app type="star" corresp="#0578031"><lem wit="【大】">尼</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">尼曰</rdg></app>。</p>
<lb n="0578c02" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0578c0201" cb:type="dharani">者𡅏者𡅏<note place="inline">一</note>者囉<note n="0578042" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">𠼐＝哩引二【三】【甲】</note><note n="0578042" resp="CBETA" type="mod">𠼐【大】，哩引二【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0578042"><lem wit="【大】">𠼐</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">哩引二</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0578c03" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0578c0301">爾時毘樓博叉天王亦白佛言。我亦以佛神
<lb n="0578c04" ed="T"/>力故。令一切眾生除非命故說陀羅<app type="star" corresp="#0578031"><lem wit="【大】">尼</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">尼曰</rdg></app>。</p>
<lb n="0578c05" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0578c0501" cb:type="dharani">未臨<note place="inline">一</note><note n="0578043" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">麼麼麼＝嚩嚩嚩嚩二【三】【甲】</note><note n="0578043" resp="CBETA" type="mod">麼麼麼【大】，嚩嚩嚩嚩二【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0578043"><lem wit="【大】">麼麼麼</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">嚩嚩嚩嚩二</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0578c06" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0578c0601">佛告四天王言。若有讀誦此經。日日受持乃
<lb n="0578c07" ed="T"/>至一遍。<note n="0578044" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">當＋（應）【三】【甲】</note><note n="0578044" resp="CBETA" type="mod">當【大】，當應【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0578044"><lem wit="【大】">當</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">當應</rdg></app>敬彼善男子善女人。應如佛想終
<lb n="0578c08" ed="T"/>不墮三惡道定增壽命。若人每日。為一切眾
<lb n="0578c09" ed="T"/>生轉<note n="0578045" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">讀＝誦【三】【甲】</note><note n="0578045" resp="CBETA" type="mod">讀【大】，誦【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0578045"><lem wit="【大】">讀</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">誦</rdg></app>此經。終無夭死短命之怖。亦無惡夢
<lb n="0578c10" ed="T"/>魘魅呪。<note n="0578046" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">咀＝詛【三】【甲】</note><note n="0578046" resp="CBETA" type="mod">咀【大】，詛【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0578046"><lem wit="【大】">咀</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">詛</rdg></app>惡形羅剎鬼神之怖。亦不為水火
<lb n="0578c11" ed="T"/>兵毒之所傷害。一切諸佛菩薩攝受護念其
<lb n="0578c12" ed="T"/>處。亦為佛所護持。爾時世尊說是經已。毘沙
<lb n="0578c13" ed="T"/>門天王等一切大眾。皆大歡喜信受奉行。</p>
<lb n="0578c14" ed="T"/><cb:juan n="001" fun="close"><cb:jhead><note n="0578047" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔佛說〕－【宋】【元】</note><note n="0578047" resp="CBETA" type="mod">佛說【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】</note><app n="0578047"><lem wit="【大】">佛說</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>一切如來金剛壽命陀羅尼經<note n="0578048" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">此下甲本奧書曰貞享三年九月十七日點校了淨嚴四十八載，元祿十六年正月二十九日以淨嚴和上之本再校了尊教</note></cb:jhead></cb:juan></cb:div>
</body></text></TEI>